panels.summary: A significant portion of inspections are pending (41%), which is higher than the number of passed (23%) or failed (36%) inspections, highlighting a potential bottleneck in the inspection process.
panels.description: Distribution of inspection results (Pass, Fail, Pending).

panels.sql: SELECT data->>'SKU' as sku, data->>'Product type' as product_type, (data->>'Revenue generated')::numeric as revenue FROM dataset_rows WHERE dataset_id = '4e7acb20-b58a-49fc-a87d-8bbb1e14cff9' ORDER BY (data->>'Revenue generated')::numeric DESC LIMIT 10
panels.title: Top 10 Products by Revenue
panels.summary: The top 10 products by revenue include a mix of haircare, cosmetics, and skincare, with SKU51 (haircare) leading at $9,866.47, suggesting a diverse range of high-performing products.
panels.description: Top 10 products with the highest revenue generated.
